show.title: Billion Dollar Waiter

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/m3CL5G
show.description: On the day of her wedding, Riya Kashyap’s world shatters when she discovers her fiancé cheating with her step-sister, who wants to steal both her love and her family empire. A year later, destiny leads Riya to Vedant Mehra — India’s richest businessman disguised as a simple waiter. What begins as a desperate lie soon turns into a high-stakes contract marriage, where love, betrayal, and hidden identities collide.
